These files were taken from the Linux Kernel Configuration System
at commit eb90251da56385cc6d485ea5e22573eba7a4b8e7
and modified for the OpenWrt Buildroot:
 - adjusted the Makefile to compile outside the kernel
 - removed gconf, tests and kernel configuration targets
 - added a 'reset' command to reset config when the target changes
 - allow config reading from & writing to a diffferent file
For a full list of changes, see the repository at:
https://github.com/cotequeiroz/linux/commits/openwrt-b2c55d50f8/scripts/kconfig
